longBusinessSummary: Rakon Limited, together with its subsidiaries, designs, manufactures, and sells frequency control and timing solutions for various applications in Asia, North America, Europe, and internationally. The company provides crystal resonators, such as tuning fork crystals, space crystals, and standard SMD crystals; and oven-controlled crystal oscillators, oven-controlled surface acoustic wave (SAW) oscillators, temperature compensated crystal oscillators, voltage controlled crystal and SAW oscillators, crystal oscillators, and voltage controlled oscillators. It also offers a range of crystal filters, including bandpass filters, notch/stop band filters, linear phase or constant group delay filters, phase and/or amplitude matching filters, and monolithic filters; and master reference oscillators, transceivers, phase locked oscillators, subsystems, digital synthesizer modules, and frequency multipliers. The company's products are used in telecommunications, space, defence, positioning, automotive, Internet of Things, and automation and control applications. In addition, it is involved in the provision of financing and marketing support services; and research and development activities. Rakon Limited was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Auckland, New Zealand.
